<body class="bg-blue-50 h-screen flex justify-center items-center flex-col">

<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-10 ml-12">Qu'allez-vous retrouver ici :</h1>

<div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap items-start mb-4 max-w-5xl ml-12">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-xl shadow-md mb-4 mr-4">
